<br>
Now we clear to the bridge, invis up, have a rogue disarm the trap, then run like mad into the castle and hole up in the lefthand room, then kill the rest of the way in.  Sometimes it works, sometimes it doesn't.  It helps immensely to have a rogue that isn't KOS so the trap doesn't wipe the raid if he trips it, as it does to have a monk puller that isn't KOS.  Makes pulling the king room a lot easier, and CR too.  The faction work sucks, but it's worth it, IMO.  Just stay FD after a pull and you won't get faction hits. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1776.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1776.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1776.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1776.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.threadControl?topicID=1776.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1776.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1776.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td